<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Wanderlust | Feature Coming Soon</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #ff4b6e;
      --gradient: linear-gradient(120deg, #fbecec, #ffe8e8);
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--gradient);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .background-animation {
      position: absolute;
      width: 180%;
      height: 180%;
      top: -40%;
      left: -40%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #ffdbe4, transparent 60%),
                  radial-gradient(circle at 70% 70%, #ffebf0, transparent 60%);
      animation: floatBG 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    @keyframes floatBG {
      0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      100% { transform: translate(50px, 60px); }
    }

    .card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      padding: 50px 40px;
      max-width: 550px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .icon {
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: bounce 2s infinite;
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      color: #222;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .loader {
      border: 5px solid #f0f0f0;
      border-top: 5px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
    }

    .btn {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 75, 110, 0.3);
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #e04360;
      transform: scale(1.04);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(255, 75, 110, 0.4);
    }

    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }

    @keyframes spin {
      0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .card {
        padding: 40px 25px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .btn {
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="background-animation"></div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">ðŸš§</div>
    <h1>Feature Coming Soon</h1>
    <p>We're currently building something exceptional for your journey. This feature will be available shortly. Stay tuned!</p>
    <div class="loader"></div>
    <a href="https://wanderlust-txqk.onrender.com/listings" class="btn">Back to Listings</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
